lastCommitMessage: feat: improve localization and user feedback in staking page
- Enhanced localization for various text strings in the staking page, providing better accessibility for English and Traditional Chinese users.
- Updated user prompts, error messages, and labels to improve clarity and user experience during staking operations.
- Refactored countdown and status display to utilize localized strings, ensuring consistent terminology throughout the staking process.
These changes contribute to a more user-friendly and inclusive interface for managing staking activities.
